               <msContents>
                  <summary>[Part of Text I-1 from Ms. MGM-008]
 I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of
                     Jesus” (fols. 120ra-125vb) 
 I-1) Introduction, incomplete [the beginning
                     and the end of the text is in MGM-008]
 - On John the Evangelist as the
                     author of the book, on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols.
                     120ra-121ra, 122, 124) 
 - Story of the family of Adam (fols. 121ra-vb,
                     123, 125).</summary>
                  
               </msContents>
